Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.27,1:17:59.03,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}缓缓地展开一面世界
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.49,1:18:04.16,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}紧闭的心也慢慢打开
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.42,1:18:10.85,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}超越那不知何时
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.72,1:18:17.63,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}听到的绝望之音
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.52,1:18:21.56,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}虚无缥缈而又耀眼
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.86,1:18:24.80,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}那惹人怜爱的微笑
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.02,1:18:29.96,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}不禁让我想要保护它
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.76,1:18:34.69,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}哭出来吧 已经没有关系了
