Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.46,1:18:44.34,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}汇集这与生俱来的软弱
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.46,1:18:47.38,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}朝着明天踏出脚步
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.50,1:18:50.89,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}让我们一起前行吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.27,1:18:54.85,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}朝着那开端
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.29,1:18:58.34,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}若能双手紧握…
