Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.40,1:19:20.83,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}寻找着无法到达的未来
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.88,1:19:28.43,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}迷惑将会化作寂寞
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.04,1:19:33.98,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}焦急地去寻求回答
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.88,1:19:40.13,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}存在于你心中的温柔
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.45,1:19:46.37,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}美丽却又沉寂着的愿望
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.84,1:19:54.46,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}让哭泣着分享痛苦的两个人一起
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.67,1:19:59.80,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}朝着目标前行吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.27,1:20:04.26,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.34,1:20:07.66,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}在那里醒来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.00,1:20:14.03,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}想要率直地相信那份温暖
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.13,1:20:17.04,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}能够变得坚强吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.14,1:20:20.32,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}投向我的眼神
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.88,1:20:28.01,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}永远地 轻轻地抱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP CHI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}
